		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm told the Wii piracy community has tools to inject an iNES format ROM into the Virtual Console NES emulator. I haven't tried it, but if it's anything like the emulator in Animal Crossing for GameCube, there will be audio problems. The electrocution sound in Balloon Fight is much more boring (muffled, no detune) in AC's emulator.

		

		</td>
